OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FWatch the Bring Your Own Baby Choir
OL,8,FThe woman behind the Bring Your Own
OL,9,FBaby Choir in Bristol says that the
OL,10,Fnew park licensing scheme means that
OL,11,Fshe is struggling to make the group
OL,12,Fviable.
OL,14,FSince Wednesday 1 April, people
OL,15,Frunning commercial activities in parks
OL,16,For green spaces managed by Bristol
OL,17,FCity Council need a parks business
OL,18,Flicence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
