PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775106076
OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FJulia Turner, who founded the BYOB
OL,7,FChoir, says she now has to pay the
OL,8,Fcouncil #410 each year to run her
OL,9,Fsmall-scale singing group for mothers
OL,10,Fand babies.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV West Country, she
OL,13,Fsaid: "The amount of people that comes
OL,14,Freally fluctuates, so the charge is
OL,15,Fjust one more thing that makes it
OL,16,Fharder to carry on doing what I'm
OL,17,Fdoing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775106076
OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,F"I feel like we've not been seen. I
OL,7,Ffeel like this is something that
OL,8,Fshould be subsidised rather than
OL,9,Ftaxed, because mothers' mental health
OL,10,Fis just so important."
OL,12,FMs Turner added: "I just want this
OL,13,Fsort of stuff to be respected."
OL,15,FBristol City Council has said the
OL,16,Flicensing scheme helps ensure
OL,17,Fbusinesses running paidfor activities
OL,18,Fmeet required standards, including
OL,19,Fappropriate insurance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
