OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FAs well as a oneoff application fee
OL,7,Fof #50 + VAT, businesses using a
OL,8,Fsingle park must pay #400 + VAT,
OL,9,Frising to #600 + VAT for those using
OL,10,Fseven parks, and for eight to 15 parks
OL,11,Fthe cost becomes #800 + VAT. These
OL,12,Fprices are reduced for dog walkers.
OL,14,FA 50% discount is offered to Bristol-
OL,15,Fbased small businesses with an annual
OL,16,Fturnover under #25,000 who operate in
OL,17,Fseven or less Bristol parks and green
OL,18,Fspaces.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
