PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775106076
OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FMs Turner argues that the scheme is
OL,7,Fflawed but says she will fight to keep
OL,8,Frunning the choir.
OL,10,FOne mother at the group said: "Being
OL,11,Foutside in nature and singing is so
OL,12,Fincredibly good for the soul. The
OL,13,Fbabies love it too. It's just really
OL,14,Fwonderful for our mental health, for
OL,15,Four wellbeing, for us and the little
OL,16,Fones."
OL,18,FAnother added: "It has been amazing to
OL,19,Fsee all the babies grow up around each
OL,20,Fother."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
