PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775106076
OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FBristol City Council says it paused
OL,7,Fthe introduction of the scheme in 2025
OL,8,Ffollowing feedback from small
OL,9,Fbusinesses, adding a review has now
OL,10,Fbeen completed, and the revised
OL,11,Fstructure is designed to be fairer,
OL,12,Fclearer, and more reflective of the
OL,13,Fdifferent types of businesses
OL,14,Foperating across the city's green
OL,15,Fspaces.
OL,17,FCllr Stephen Williams, Chair of the
OL,18,FPublic Health and Communities
OL,19,FCommittee, said the scheme is about
OL,20,Fensuring public safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
