OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1775106076
OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,FHe explained: "This is not about
OL,7,Fraising money. There are a lot of
OL,8,Fpromotional activities taking place in
OL,9,Four parks which the businesses haven't
OL,10,Fsought our permission, even though our
OL,11,Fby-laws say that they should.
OL,13,F"So we don't know whether people are
OL,14,Fqualified to deliver the service that
OL,15,Fthey are to the public. For instance,
OL,16,Fpersonal trainers really should have
OL,17,Fqualifications and we don't know if
OL,18,Fpeople are properly insured in case
OL,19,Fthings go wrong.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
