OL,3,CFeeling unseen: Baby choir charged
OL,4,Chundreds to sing in public parks
OL,6,F"So it's a license for the activity of
OL,7,Fwhich there is a fee. It's not aimed
OL,8,Fat raising lots of money for the
OL,9,Fcouncil."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
